Display instructions for manual USB setup of DualShock3:confctrl_ph.sh -p help -c usb -t PS3 | more
Display instructions for manual bluetooth setup of Dualshock3:confctrl_ph.sh -p help -c bluetooth -t PS3 | more
Setup bluetooth DualShock3 controllers:confctrl_ph.sh -p prompt -t PS3
Go to Controller Status:ph_show_menu StatusManagement_Controllers
Go to Controllers:ph_show_menu Controllers
Go to Main:ph_show_menu Main
Open a shell (Type 'CTRL-D' to return):echo;cd;/bin/bash
Quit:break
Return to previous screen:return
